n  - `workspace/ops/PROJECT_MAP.md`\n  - `workspace/ops/RUN_ALL_WORKERS.ps1`\n  - `workspace/runbooks/DAILY_OPS.md`\n- Roster includes remembered worker personas (Calvin, Albert, Sam, William, Bryer, Beckham, Saylor, Bill, Jared, Azeem, Kelly) mapped to project roles.\n- Confirmed persistent local agent dirs still only show `main`; worker roster now serves as durable relaunch map.\n- Drive links provided by user acknowledged; practical recovery path continues via mounted `G:\\My Drive\\...` inventory + copy-first restore policy.\n\n## 3:41–3:54 PM execution burst (mission-control + workers + LinkedIn Creator)\n- User requested immediate safe-merge promotion + LinkedIn Creator Studio inclusion into product path and startup.\n- Created canonical LinkedIn Creator product path and startup tooling:\n  - `projects/_merged_staging/mission-control/products/linkedin-creator-os/frontend/index.html`\n  - `projects/_merged_staging/mission-control/products/linkedin-creator-os/PRODUCTION.md`\n  - `scripts/run-linkedin-creator-local.ps1`\n- Verified folder exists and launched local server; app available at `http://127.0.0.1:8088` (background process session `gentle-claw`).\n- Fixed `ops/RUN_ALL_WORKERS.ps1` parse errors by correcting escaped apostrophes in single-quoted strings (`today''s`), then re-ran successfully.\n- Triggered active pipeline runs:\n  - `scripts/run-daily-pipeline.ps1`\n  - `scripts/mission-control-status.ps1`\n  - `scripts/build_top_opportunities.ps1`\n  - Python runs for `trend_scanner_agent.py`, `job_hunter_agent.py`, `lead_builder_agent.py`, and `job_scanner.py`\n- Latest key outputs refreshed:\n  - `deliverables/mission-control/mission_control_status.md`\n  - `deliverables/opportunities/TOP_OPPORTUNITIES_2026-03-09.md`\n  - `outputs/research/ai_money_trends.md`\n  - `outputs/jobs/daily_job_pipeline.csv`\n  - `outputs/leads/high_value_targets.csv`\n  - `job_pipeline/jobs_2026_03_09.json`\n- Replit pass executed and produced:\n  - `ops/REPLIT_FINISH_REPORT_2